      <h2>Simple Mega Menu Example</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted)">This is a lightweight, responsive mega menu built with HTML/CSS and tiny JS for mobile toggle. Use it in your TRU DIAMONDS site and customize links, images, and colors.</p>
